# Component Development Rules

Follow `docs/STYLING.md` and `docs/CODE_STYLE.md`.

## shadcn/ui Card Structure

ALWAYS use proper Card structure:

```typescript
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardDescription,
  CardFooter,
  CardHeader,
  CardTitle,
} from '@/components/ui/card';

function MyCard() {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle>Title</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Description</CardDescription>
        <Badge>Tag</Badge>
      </CardHeader>
      
      <CardContent>
        {/* Images, text, lists */}
      </CardContent>
      
      <CardFooter>
        {/* ONLY buttons and actions */}
        <Button>Action</Button>
      </CardFooter>
    </Card>
  );
}
```

## Animation Performance

NO excessive animations on cards/grids:

```typescript
// ❌ WRONG - impacts performance
<Card className="hover:scale-105 transition-transform">

// ✅ CORRECT - shadow/border only
<Card className="transition-shadow hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/50">
```

## Client Components

Add `'use client'` directive for:
- Components with hooks (useState, useEffect)
- Components with Zustand stores
- Interactive components

```typescript
'use client';

import { useCartStore } from '@/entities/cart/model/store';

export function CartButton() {
  const items = useCartStore((s) => s.items);
  // ...
}
```

